func main() {
	r := mux.NewRouter()
	r.HandleFunc("/health", getHealth).Methods("GET")
	// r.HandleFunc("/auth", controllers.GetAuth).Methods("GET")
	fmt.Println("Server is running on port 8080")
 
	ch := make(chan string)
	go func() {
		err := http.ListenAndServe(":8080", r)
		if err != nil {
			fmt.Println("Error starting server: ", err)
			return
		}
		ch <- "done"
	}()
	fmt.Println(<-ch)
}
